<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/27(Sat.)15 Health and Nutrition Benefits of Sesame Seeds/How our views on work have changed forever(Host:Kevin)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=484&amp;p=506#p506"><![CDATA[
3/27(Sat.)15 Health and Nutrition Benefits of Sesame Seeds/How our views on work have changed forever(Host:Kevin)<br /><br />Article 1:15 Health and Nutrition Benefits of Sesame Seeds<br /><a href="https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/sesame-seeds" class="postlink">https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/sesame-seeds</a><br /><br />1:What's your experiences and opinions of taking supplement products?<br />2:What kind of sesame seeds desserts you like the most?<br />3:What do you benefit from reading this article?<br /><br /><br />Article 2:How our views on work have changed forever<br /><a href="https://www.bbc.com/worklife/article/20201209-how-our-views-on-work-have-changed-forever" class="postlink">https://www.bbc.com/worklife/article/20201209-how-our-views-on-work-have-changed-forever</a><br /><br />1:Which work style do you prefer?working at home?or working with colleagues?<br />2:If you could start over, will you change your career?<br />3:For some people money is the most important thing they go to work, but the others they want to find value in their career. What's your definition of your career?<br /><br />///////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔！<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1000元 (學生:500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed Mar 24, 2021 4:48 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
